{"tid":408472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰獨立後，巴塞可能被西甲踢走，邀請巴塞落戶港超有無得諗？","createTime":"2017-09-21T08:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T11:48:54.000Z","uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8cd54ddc5942ef613fdcc877af9702cba8a1933","tid":408472,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:46:30.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區計劃於下月一日舉行獨立公投，而中央政府則認為公投違法，周二更突撃搜查加泰多個政府部門，拘捕當地多名官員。球會巴塞隆拿周三發公開信回應事件，譴責任何阻礙民主、自主以及言論自由的行為。公開信又寫道，巴塞隆拿會以文明、和平、理想的方式，繼續支持大多數加泰人民的意願。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，巴塞官方於6月曾公開支持《全民公投協議》(Pacto Nacional por el Refer&eacute;ndum），而該協議旨在取得組織或個人的聯署，以支持加泰隆尼亞舉行獨立公投。"},{"pid":"cc20c8688d2862a1a2047e218e7f70173bc29111","tid":408472,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"去法甲/中東/支那都唔會黎香港"},{"pid":"91801281468390b0a173038c7549ee2859f1c592","tid":408472,"uid":5971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話去法甲咩 係就好睇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49ecb812f837a9a3a39990e9df78d8878f37012","tid":408472,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"人地睬你都on9"},{"pid":"d8e4c6e8d40ec65fcde574ce641eae8541b9b804","tid":408472,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"去英超等梅西挑戰自己"},{"pid":"e37a2a1b329f0bbd5b6b0d25bb44265958bb0497","tid":408472,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"西甲變成新德甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241f19f86eb728913c05814a5bdda1ea89e8250f","tid":408472,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"幾年前都講過去法甲<br />\n但法足總叫佢地叫地級聯賽開始打起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2672169b6ca645ee3d7e67c3ce40dd3bf5db6468","tid":408472,"uid":5649,"l